      "author": "pfrankov",
      "description": "Completely rewritten the colorizer's algorithm, nested tags are colored with a gradient.\r\nAdded an option to reset all tag colors and recalculate from scratch, which is useful if you had a lot of tag name changes at some point.\r\n\r\n🚨 Saturation and Lightness settings are marked deprecated and will be replaced by a selector of 2-3 pre-made options.\r\n\r\nTo stay with previous plugin's version and colorizer's algorithm, use Obsidian's command `BRAT: Add a beta plugin with frozen version based on a release tag`\r\n<img width=\"550\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/pfrankov/obsidian-colored-tags/assets/584632/b3db2590-48c1-4b45-9129-f617cf877df1\">",
